{
  "video_id": "uaB6Bdgp3WU",
  "title": "Birke Baehr: What's wrong with our food system",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "Hello. My name is Birke Baehr,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m 11 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "I came here today to talk about what&#39;s wrong with our food system."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "First of all, I would like to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m really amazed at how easily kids are led to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "all the marketing and advertising"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "on TV, at public schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "and pretty much everywhere else you look."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "It seems to me like corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "are always trying to get kids, like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "to get their parents to buy stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "that really isn&#39;t good for us or the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "Little kids, especially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "are attracted by colorful packaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "and plastic toys."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "I must admit, I used to be one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "I also used to think that all of our food"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "came from these happy, little farms"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "where pigs rolled in mud and cows grazed on grass all day."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "What I discovered was this is not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "I began to look into this stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "on the Internet, in books and in documentary films,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "in my travels with my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "I discovered the dark side of the industrialized food system."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "First, there&#39;s genetically engineered seeds and organisms."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "That is when a seed is manipulated in a laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "to do something not intended by nature --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "like taking the DNA of a fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "and putting it into the DNA of a tomato. Yuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t get me wrong, I like fish and tomatoes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "but this is just creepy."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "The seeds are then planted, then grown."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "The food they produce have been proven"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "to cause cancer and other problems in lab animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "and people have been eating food produced this way"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "since the 1990s."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "And most folks don&#39;t even know they exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "Did you know rats that ate genetically engineered corn"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "had developed signs of liver and kidney toxicity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "These include kidney inflammation and lesions and increased kidney weight."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "Yet almost all the corn we eat"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "has been altered genetically in some way."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "And let me tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "corn is in everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "And don&#39;t even get me started on the Confined Animal Feeding Operations"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "called CAFOS."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "Conventional farmers use chemical fertilizers"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "made from fossil fuels"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "that they mix with the dirt to make plants grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "They do this because they&#39;ve stripped the soil from all nutrients"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "from growing the same crop over and over again."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "Next, more harmful chemicals are sprayed on fruits and vegetables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "like pesticides and herbicides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "to kill weeds and bugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "When it rains, these chemicals seep into the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "or run off into our waterways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "poisoning our water too."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "Then they irradiate our food, trying to make it last longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "so it can travel thousands of miles"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "from where it&#39;s grown to the supermarkets."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "So I ask myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "how can I change? How can I change these things?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "This is what I found out."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "I discovered that there&#39;s a movement for a better way."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "Now a while back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "I wanted to be an NFL football player."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 177260.0,
      "text": "I decided that I&#39;d rather be an organic farmer instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 177260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "And that way I can have a greater impact on the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "This man, Joel Salatin, they call him a lunatic farmer"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "because he grows against the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "Since I&#39;m home-schooled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "I went to go hear him speak one day."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "This man, this \"lunatic farmer,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t use any pesticides, herbicides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "or genetically modified seeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "And so for that, he&#39;s called crazy by the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "I want you to know that we can all make a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "by making different choices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "by buying our food directly from local farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "or our neighbors who we know in real life."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "Some people say organic or local food is more expensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "but is it really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "With all these things I&#39;ve been learning about the food system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "it seems to me that we can either pay the farmer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "or we can pay the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "Now I know definitely which one I would choose."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "I want you to know that there are farms out there --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "like Bill Keener in Sequatchie Cove Farm in Tennessee --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "whose cows do eat grass"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "and whose pigs do roll in the mud, just like I thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I go to Bill&#39;s farm and volunteer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "so I can see up close and personal"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "where the meat I eat comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "I want you to know that I believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "kids will eat fresh vegetables and good food"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "if they know more about it and where it really comes from."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "I want you to know that there are farmers&#39; markets"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "in every community popping up."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "I want you to know that me, my brother and sister"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "actually like eating baked kale chips."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "I try to share this everywhere I go."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "Not too long ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "my uncle said that he offered my six-year-old cousin cereal."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "He asked him if he wanted organic Toasted O&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "or the sugarcoated flakes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "you know, the one with the big striped cartoon character on the front."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "My little cousin told his dad"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "that he would rather have the organic Toasted O&#39;s cereal"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "because Birke said he shouldn&#39;t eat sparkly cereal."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "And that, my friends, is how we can make a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "one kid at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "So next time you&#39;re at the grocery store, think local,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "choose organic, know your farmer and know your food."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}